%h2 Recurring Charge Categories

%p.lead 
	These are the most common types of recurring charges.  Select the categories which apply to you and we'll help you identify charges in those categories to track with trym.

=simple_form_for current_user, url: wizard_path, method: :put do |f|
	.row
		-TrymCategory.recurring.in_groups_of(5, false) do |category_group|
			.col-md-6
				-category_group.each do |category|
					.checkbox.wizard-checkbox
						%label
							=wizard_charge_category_checkboxes(category, @category_ids)

	.row.charge-wizard-actions
		.col-xs-2
			=link_to "Back", wizard_path(:link_or_manual), class: "btn btn-default"
		.col-xs-10.text-right
			=f.submit "Next", class: "btn btn-primary"

%div{style: "min-height: 20px;"}
	